<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="Install_BDIITutorial"></a>  <strong>Install BDIITutorial</strong> </h1>
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Installation"> Installation</a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Introduction"> Introduction</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Create_Directories"> Create Directories</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Download_and_install_rpms_for_bd"> Download and install rpms for bdii</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Download_and_install_other_files"> Download and install other files</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Create_symlinks"> Create symlinks</a>
